#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:16
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>gopher</command> began as a distributed campus information service "
"at the University of Minnesota. Gopher allows the user to access information "
"on Gopher servers running on Internet hosts."
msgstr ""
"Gopher se je pričekl kot razširjeni univerzitetni informacijski servis na "
"Univerzi v Minnesoti. Gopher omogoča uporabnikom dostop do podatkov na "
"strežnikih Gopher, ki tečejo na internetnih gostiteljih."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Gopher is an Internet information browsing service that uses a menu-driven "
"interface. Users select information from menus, which may return another "
"menu or display a text file. An item may reside on a Gopher server you "
"originally queried, or it may be on another Gopher server (or another host). "
"Gopher can <quote>tunnel</quote> from one Gopher to another without the user "
"knowing that the server and/or host machine have changed. Gopher keeps the "
"exact location of computers hidden from the user, providing the "
"<quote>illusion</quote> of a single, large set of interconnected menus."
msgstr ""
"Gopher je storitev brskanja po internetnih informacijah, ki uporablja "
"menijsko vodenvmesnik. Uporabniki izberejo informacije iz menijev, ki lahko "
"vrnejo druge menije ali prikaz besedilne datoteke. Element se lahko nahaja "
"na vašem strežniku Gopher prvotno zahtevano ali pa je na drugem strežniku "
"Gopher (ali drugem gostitelju).Gopher lahko <quote>tunelira</quote> od enega "
"Gopherja do drugega brez uporabnikače veste, da sta se strežnik in/ali "
"gostiteljski stroj spremenila. Gopher ohranja natančno  lokacijo "
"računalnikov, skrita pred uporabnikom, ki zagotavlja <quote>Iluzijo</quote> "
"enega samega velikega nabora med seboj povezanih menijev."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Gopher permits the user to record an item's location in a <quote>bookmark</"
"quote> thereby allowing users to follow a <quote>bookmark</quote> directly "
"to a particular item without searching the menu system. Gopher menus are not "
"standardized, inasmuch as each Gopher server is individually determined."
msgstr ""
"Gopher dovoljuje uporabniku, da zabeleži lokacijo elementa v "
"<quote>zaznamku</quote> in tako uporabnikom omogoča neposredno sledenje "
"<quote>zaznamka</quote>na določen element brez iskanja po sistemu menijev. "
"Gopher meniji niso standardizirani, saj je vsak strežnik Gopher individualno "
"določen."

